{"tid":1340003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗警察 港鐵必須為元朗事件必須負上責任","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:11:56.000Z","uid":68194,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7dde3e6850e936c8193affd0390060ea7fc470e5","tid":1340003,"uid":68194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"港鐵有咩理由可以俾一大堆白衫恐怖分子衝入地鐵站亂咁打義士?<br />\n警察叫你封站就咁快 你唔可以用返壓力叫防暴警察?<br />\n有幾多市民因為今次俾人打到仆街，有心理陰影，港鐵難辭其咎。<br />\n港鐵必須要向今次事件受影響嘅人賠償，管理層都要下台。<br />\n今次事件完全暴露香港制度有幾咁腐敗<br />\n成件事根本係警察、黑社會同港鐵打曬籠通<br />\n牛屎佬、黑警死全家唔在講，要光復我都一定會去<br />\n但大家唔好忽略港鐵有幾咁垃圾"},{"pid":"2c718999f49eb2538c621f5f1a80369e3b11c0ae","tid":1340003,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855b772aaa2c0ce9e5b023607dcb5c4dfa4aba17","tid":1340003,"uid":68194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"44557882fada9858901f316410092f127d8f38f2","tid":1340003,"uid":68194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ee62ddd59c714aa2f1db8845be8586f1d4af040","tid":1340003,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:59.000Z","msg":"職員都俾人打"},{"pid":"7be285112d11b8f84a8d4523d08d59843af13c80","tid":1340003,"uid":109538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"港鐵本身做唔到d咩"},{"pid":"9fd1103eb7714